1. Extracts "title" from FormData: `formData.get("title") as string`
2. Calls `addTodoWithDb(db, title ?? "")`
3. This is the actual server action bound to the form

The design separates business logic (`addTodoWithDb`) from the server action wrapper (`addTodo`) to enable testing with a custom database instance.

